(1, 'adventure,nature,honeymoon', 'goa', '2023-05-24', 'ahmedabad', 'goa', 'package_imgs/ishvani-hans-xWFL4KNd_2A-unsplash.jpg', 'The Goa package offers a fun-filled vacation for beach lovers and history enthusiasts. It includes four days of exploration and relaxation, with activities like beach hopping, water sports, a tour of Old Goa\'s churches and temples, and a visit to the Spice Plantations and Dudhsagar Waterfalls. The package provides accommodation at a comfortable hotel and transportation for sightseeing, making your trip hassle-free and enjoyable.', 20000, 5, 4, 'Arrival in Goa', 'Upon arrival in Goa, you will be greeted by our representative and transferred to your hotel. After check-in, you can spend the day at leisure exploring the nearby area or relaxing on the beach.', 'Sightseeing in Goa', 'After breakfast, you will head out for a sightseeing tour of Goa. You will visit popular tourist attractions such as the Basilica of Bom Jesus, Se Cathedral, and the famous Mangueshi Temple. You will also have the opportunity to enjoy a river cruise on the Mandovi River in the evening.', 'Day at Leisure', 'Today is a free day to explore Goa on your own. You can spend time at the beach or indulge in adventure activities such as parasailing, jet skiing or banana boat rides.', 'North Goa Beaches Tour', 'After breakfast, you will embark on a North Goa Beaches tour where you will visit popular beaches such as Calangute, Anjuna, and Baga. You can spend time relaxing on the beach, trying out water sports or enjoying the beach shacks.', 'Departure from Goa', 'After breakfast, you will check out from the hotel and be transferred to the airport or railway station for your journey back to Ahmedabad.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 0, 0, 1, 0),
(2, 'adventure', 'memorable manali', '2023-04-26', 'ahmedabad', 'manali', 'package_imgs/bg4.jpg', 'Manali is the most destination place to visit in India. Manali is a hill station in Himacahl Pradesh. Manali has a magical draw for travelers due to its beautiful topography, abundant flora, and exquisite vistas. Sitting on the picturesque Beas River valley, the blooming township of Manali prides itself in its perfect blend of nature and culture. It is a like fairy-tale snow-capped mountain landscapes, flower-covered meadows and glaciers, flowing rivers, temples, and Buddhist monasteries. The snowfall atop the towering Rohtang Pass will be a memorable experience. The tour of Manali includes the some amazing things like Skiing and snowboarding are among them, as are hiking, paragliding, rock climbing, canoeing, mountain biking, and white-water rafting. The tour includes the snow-fed Beas runs through the heart of the city, separating the town from its counterpart,', 25000, 3, 4, 'delhi to shimla', 'Start your wonderful journey to Manali by boarding the Volvo from Delhi Volvo pick up point (Guests are requested to report at scheduled time). Overnight Journey will be by Volvo. Exotic Manali offers something special for everyone. It gives peace to mediators; inspiration to artists, daring Activities for adventure Seekers and this list just goes on. As soon as you will enter into the terrains of Manali, you will feel cool breeze already taking all your stress away and surprising you from its jaw- dropping landscapes.', 'solang valley', 'Upon reaching Manali Stop, our team will greet you and transfer you to the hotel (Check In time will be as per Hotel Policy and early check-in will be subject to availability and extra cost). After fresh up enjoy Manali local sightseeing tour. Start your trip by covering Hadimba Devi Temple and Ghatotkacha Temple. The temples are dedicated to Mata Hadimba (the most worshipped deity in Himacahl) and her son Ghatotkacha. Clubhouse will be next place to visit. Here, enjoy recreational activities such as Skating, disco, zip line, TT and much more. By evening you will be escort back to hotel, have dinner and stay overnight at the hotel of Manali.', 'day at naggar', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Manali’s hotel. Today you will be taking a day tour to Solang Valley (15 Kms from Manali) summers or winters, this place never fails to fascinate the visitors. Summers offer enchanting greenery all around whereas the winters are blessed with amazing snowfalls.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 1, 0),
(3, 'adventure', 'Tour Of Manali', '2023-05-01', 'delhi', 'manali', 'package_imgs/paragliding-in-solang.jpg', 'Manali is one of the most famous destinations all over the Himachal Pradesh. Manali is the perfect holiday for an excursion to the hills. One of the most popular hill stations in India, Manali is situated in the middle of the mountain slopes, with the most beautiful and pleasant views, charming streams, and fairytale-like fog surrounding little cottages. The natural beauty of the surroundings, serene atmosphere and beautiful views will make you feel completely relax and rejuvenated on your vacation. Manali Luxury tour package has a Lush valleys, snow-capped mountains, magnificent lakes, old shrines, abundant fauna and numerous adventure activities make up the allure of Manali. Bharat booking Holidays is giving you an amazing opportunity to try out these thrilling activities and explore every aspect of this picturesque town. In this trip you can enjoy the magnificent views of snow-capped mountains and try thrilling activities like snow-scooter rides, skiing, mountain biking, Zorbing and paragliding. Luxury tour of Manali has a place to visit the Solang and Kullu Valleys and Manikaran temple and hot springs. In the tour of Manali, you will experience the cool breeze already taking all your stress away, soothing you from the serene environment and surprising you with its jaw-downed landscapes. The Luxury trip of Manali will give you an amazing and unforgettable memory in life.\r\nThe Luxury itinerary has planned in a way that you won’t miss out any places (3N 4D), must visit the Himachal Luxury package to get the new things in life with a great memories.', 11999, 4, 3, 'delhi-manali', 'Upon arrival at Delhi station our executive will receive you with warm welcome. Begin your wonderful vacation in Himachal starting from Manali. Reach Manali within 15 hours and check in into the hotel. Spend the evening exploring the place on your own. Have dinner & Overnight stay.', 'manali local', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Manali’s hotel. Today you will be taking a day tour to Manali’s local sightseeing. Proceed for Manali local sightseeing tour. Start your day by covering Hadimba Devi Temple and Ghatotkacha Temple. The temples are dedicated to Mata Hadimba (the most worshipped deity in Himachal) and her son Ghatotkacha. Clubhouse will be the next place to visit. Here, enjoy recreational activities such as Skating, Zip line, Table Tennis and much more. Later bathe yourselves in Sage Vashisht’s Hot Springs containing Medical properties (Do carry a towel). Right across the Hot spring are temples of Lord Shiva and Lord Ram. By evening you will b escort back to hotel, have dinner and stay overnight at the hotel of Manali.', 'solang valley', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Manali’s hotel. Today you will be taking a day tour to Solang Valley (15 Kms from Manali) summers or winters, this place never fails to fascinate the visitors. Summers offer enchanting greenery all around whereas the winters are blessed with amazing snowfalls. While visiting Solang Valley one should also try their hands on adventure activities as it is one of best place for adventures near Manali. You can enjoy activities like Paragliding, Cable Car Rope way; Zorbing, Snow Scooter, Skiing, Horse Riding, and also can enjoy a short Trek to Anjani Mahadev. By evening you will be escort back to hotel after a joyful experience and have your dinner with overnight stay at hotel of Manali. Winter Note: During Snowfall Solang valley sightseeing point will be covered if weather, road condition is clear and possibilities of vehicle to reach there, otherwise sightseeing up to Barrier Point will be provided.', 'departure to delhi', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Shimla’s hotel then check out from the hotel of Manali. Today you will be taking back to Delhi for departure with wonderful memories.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 1, 0),
(4, 'nature', 'Himachal Harmony Luxury', '2023-05-15', 'ahmedabad', 'manali', 'package_imgs/download_9.jpg', 'Himacahl is a destination all over the India which has its natural beauty with amazing places. A large number of tourists have led to the exploitation of Himachal Pradesh as a tourist destination. The majestic snow clad mountains, stunningly rich greenery and the beautiful lakes in the land of Himachal Pradesh greet you to enjoy their timeless beauty. Himachal Luxury tour is endowed with clear and serene lakes, lofty mountains, ancient temples and cheerful people who are as innocent as nature itself. Home to the best of the tourist destinations like Kullu, Manali, Dharamshala, Chamba and Shimla, Himachal is paradise on earth inviting an onslaught of tourists. The natural beauty of Himachal along with the hills and valleys add peace to your holiday while the pilgrimages make it serene and divine. With spectacular snowy peaks and plunging river valleys, beautiful Himachal is India’s outdoor adventure playground. From trekking and climbing to rafting, paragliding and skiing, if it can be done in the mountains, it can be done here. The tour includes the adventure activities, including mountaineering, rock climbing, trekking, rafting, paragliding, ice skating, and skiing, which offer unique experiences. From quaint villages to verdant valleys, Himachal Pradesh is a paradise for nature lovers and thrill-seekers. Himachal Pradesh is one of the most popular destinations in India where You can enjoy the beauty of nature and get away from the hustle and bustle of city life. Hill stations appeal with a holiday atmosphere and colonial echoes, while backpacker magnets lure with chilled-out vibes and mountain beauty. The luxury tour of Himachal Harmony is Makes your holiday an unforgettable with a great and an amazing memory.\r\nThe Luxury itinerary has planned in a way that you won’t miss out any places (5N 6D), must visit the Shimla with Manali Himachal Luxury package to get the new things in life with a great memories.', 19999, 6, 5, 'ahmedabad-manali', 'Upon arrival at ahm. station our executive will receive you with warm welcome. Begin your wonderful vacation in Himachal starting from Shimla. Arrival at Shimla, check-in into the pre-booked hotel for Overnight stay. Dinner & Overnight stay at the hotel. Shimla is renowned as the Queen of Hills because of its mesmerizing sceneries and colonial heritage and has retained its charm since British India time to till now.', 'shimla-kufri+local', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Shimla’s hotel. Today you will be taking a day tour to Shimla local with Kufri. Proceed to Kufri (22 Kms from Shimla). Kufri is all season place – winters are packed with snow adventures while the summers are brimmed with colourful meadows. Kufri also has a Himalayan Wildlife Zoo and Kufri Fun Park which will make the trip even more exciting (Entry & Activities at your own cost). After sightseeing head back to Shimla. In the city we will visit Indian Institute of Advance Study, Also you will cover Places by walking The Mall, Johnnie’s Wax Museum, Scandal Point, Ridge, Gaiety Theatre, Heritage Museum, Lakkar Bazaar, Rani Jhansi Park and Christ Church. By evening you will be escort back to hotel, have dinner and stay overnight at the hotel of Shimla.', 'shimla-kullu-manali', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Shimla’s hotel then check out from the hotel of Shimla. Today you will be taking Kullu Manali. On the way catch glimpses of Vaishno Devi Temple, Hanogi Mata Temple, and Pandoh Dam & Sunder Nagar Lake. Near Kullu, we will be visiting Pashmina Shawl showrooms and will try out our hands on White Water River Rafting too. Arrival and check-in into the hotel in Manali. Overnight stay will be in hotel.', 'manali local', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Manali’s hotel. Today you will be taking a day tour to Manali’s local sightseeing. Proceed for Manali local sightseeing tour. Start your day by covering Hadimba Devi Temple and Ghatotkacha Temple. The temples are dedicated to Mata Hadimba (the most worshipped deity in Himachal) and her son Ghatotkacha. Clubhouse will be the next place to visit. Here, enjoy recreational activities such as Skating, Zip line, Table Tennis and much more. Later bathe yourselves in Sage Vashisht’s Hot Springs containing Medical properties (Do carry a towel). Right across the Hot spring are temples of Lord Shiva and Lord Ram. By evening you will b escort back to hotel, have dinner and stay overnight at the hotel of Manali.', 'Solang Valley', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Manali’s hotel. Today you will be taking a day tour to Solang Valley (15 Kms from Manali) summers or winters, this place never fails to fascinate the visitors. Summers offer enchanting greenery all around whereas the winters are blessed with amazing snowfalls. While visiting Solang Valley one should also try their hands on adventure activities as it is one of best place for adventures near Manali. You can enjoy activities like Paragliding, Cable Car Rope way; Zorbing, Snow Scooter, Skiing, Horse Riding, and also can enjoy a short Trek to Anjani Mahadev. By evening you will be escort back to hotel after a joyful experience and have your dinner with overnight stay at hotel of Manali. Winter Note: During Snowfall Solang valley sightseeing point will be covered if weather, road condition is clear and possibilities of vehicle to reach there, otherwise sightseeing up to Barrier Point will be provided.', 'departure to ahmedabad', 'Have a healthy breakfast at the Manali’s hotel then check out from the hotel of Manali. Today you will be taking back to Delhi for departure with wonderful memories.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 1, 0),
(5, 'honeymoon', 'Pink City With Ajmer', '2023-05-27', 'gujarat', 'rajasthan', 'package_imgs/image.jpg', 'Rajasthan is filled with rich culture, heritage, and royalty that make it perfect place for the people to enjoy your holiday. The exciting Jaipur to Ajmer-Pushkar tour that will surely make you fall in love with these places, while you have the vacation. The vibrant city of Jaipur is brimming with colors, enchanting forts, and mesmerizing markets. The Jaipur called as the “Pink City”. It is the capital of the historically rich state of Rajasthan in India. The Architectural marvels of the city reveal its glorious past. From the captivating Hawa Mahal to the bewitching City Palace and it is famous for its beautiful handicrafts and jewelry which are unique to the city. Ajmer is famous for its ancient Shrine of the Sufi Saint Khwaja Moinuddin Chishti. Ajmer and Pushkar is well known for its Lord Brahma’s ancient temple and Pushkar Lake.  Pink city with Ajmer-Pushkar includes a great safari and camping site on the desert. It organizes the world camel festival every year which is the most talked about. Jeep safari along with camel safari is also a great pastime and activity to do in leisure time. A detour to Ajmer will bring you close to the world-famous Ajmer Sharif. Our Ajmer Pushkar tour from Jaipur brings you a plethora of activities tailored to give your holidays a cultural boost. Ajmer is an ancient pilgrimage site that has now turned into a public place and is a visit by people of all from all over the world as a popular tourist place. Make a plan to visit Rajasthan to explore these places to get the new experience.\r\n\r\nThe itinerary has planned in a way that you won’t miss out any places (3N 4D), must visit to explore the Pink City with Ajmer/Pushkar.', 15999, 4, 3, 'arrival in jaipur', 'Upon arrival at Jaipur station, our executive will receive you with warm welcome. You will be taking to your Hotel. Reach in Hotel. Have some rest in hotel late visit to Albert Hall (Museum), Birla Mandir, Chokhi Dhani (Restaurant). Later you will be escort back to hotel and stay overnight at the hotel in Jaipur. Jaipur is also called the Pink City Jaipur is the capital of the royal state of Rajasthan. Along with Delhi and Agra, Jaipur forms the Golden Triangle and hails as one of the most famous tourist circuits in the country. Rajputs ruled Jaipur for many centuries and developed it as a planned city in the 17th century AD. With the old city surrounded by walls and gates decorated with drawings on the backdrop of a beautiful pink hue, Jaipur, the pink city, successfully retains its old-world charm. Home to a few UNESCO World Heritage sites, including Amer Fort and Jantar Mantar, Jaipur holds many magnificent forts, palaces, temples and museums and brims with bustling local bazaars where you can shop to your heart\'s content. The city is also very well known for its local food, and the most famous dishes include the Ghewar, Pyaaz Kachori and Dal Baati Churma. The city also hosts the Jaipur Literary Festival, which is Asia\'s biggest festival of its kind. Note: Any monument fee & adventure activities cost will be charged on the spot by own.', 'Jaipur Sightseeing', 'Begin your day with a healthy breakfast. Today you will be taking a day tour to Jaipur Sightseeing. The entire royal family of Jaipur resides in the resplendent Jaipur City Palace, better known as the Maharaja Sawai Man Singh II Museum, part of which is also open to the public, Jantar Mantar (Stone Observatory), Hawa Mahal: Hawa Mahal is famous because of its amazing and unique architecture. 953 windows or jharokhas are beautifully incorporated in the honeycomb design of this palace. In addition to providing a window to the outside world for the royal women, these windows helped in keeping the palace airy and cool, Jal Mahal & Amber Fort: Amber Fort is known for its artistic style elements. With its large ramparts and series of gates and cobbled paths, the fort overlooks Maota Lake, which is the main source of water for the Amber Palace. Mughal architecture greatly influenced the architectural style of several buildings of the fort. By 6 Pm you will be escort back to hotel and stay overnight at the hotel in Jaipur.', 'excursion to  Ajmer+Pushkar', 'Begin your day with a healthy breakfast. Today you will be taking a day tour to Ajmer+Pushkar. Arrive & Visit Ajmer-e-Sharif Dargah, Adhai-Din-Ka Jhonpra, Ana Sagar Lake & drive to Pushkar, visit various Temples and Ghats and holy Pushkar Lake. There are more than 400 hundred temples in Pushkar but the main attraction being the temple of Lord Brahma, the only temple in India dedicated to Brahma. Pushkar is also famous for its annual fair (Pushkar Camel Fair) featuring a trading fete of cattle, horses and camels. It is held over seven days in autumn marking Kartika Purnima according to the Hindu calendar (Kartik (month), October or November). It attracts nearly 200,000 people. Later you will be escort back to hotel in Jaipur overnight stay at hotel in Jaipur.', 'hotel-jaipur airport/railway', 'After a healthy breakfast check out from the hotel of Jaipur. Our representative will take you to station for drop and Depart with lovely memories and beautiful experiences.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 1, 0),
(6, 'nature', 'nature of kerala tour', '2023-05-25', 'ahmedabad', 'kerala', 'package_imgs/download_9_rIdMgiO.jpg', 'Kerala is classified as paradise on the Earth. Kerala is a state that has perfect mix touristic pleasures. The sublime beaches, cultural richness, historic depth, exotic wildlife, and beautiful mountainsides promise and always deliver an unforgettable gateway. Kerala has a unique culture of the region which must be witnessed. There are plenty of festivals celebrated here. Kerala has the rich couture all over the world. The trip Visit Kerala and See Astounding Places will give you the most amazing place to visit and to explore the most beautiful place. Located in the Western Ghats of Kerala, Munnar is popular for stunning viewpoints and verdant tea estates. The trip of Astounding will allow you to explore the natural and culture at wealth of Kerala. In this trip you will be enjoying an activities such like boating, wildlife safari is, tea estate visits and nature walks. The trip has included the Kochi which is really attractive and you can wander around in Fort Kochi and the colonial architecture, admire the wall paintings of Mattancherry Palace and wander around Marine. Must visit to Kerala explore the most astounding places over the Kerala, the tour of will give you the most amazing experience.\r\nThe itinerary has planned in a way that you won’t miss out any places (3N 4D), must visit the Kerala to feel the Astounding places.', 21999, 4, 3, 'arriving at god\'s own country', 'Upon arrival at Kochi station our executive will receive you with warm welcome. You will be taking to hotel in Munnar. Enjoy the scenic road journey to the beautiful hill-station of Munnar as you pass by some eye-catching natural beauty exemplified by wonderful Valara and Cheeyappara waterfalls. Upon arrival in Munnar, complete the check-in procedure at your hotel and then get to relax and unwind. Rest of the first day of your in Munnar is at leisure which you can choose to spend your way. The day ends with a comfortable overnight stay at the hotel in Munnar.', 'exploring the wild side of kerala', 'After a healthy breakfast check out from the hotel of Munnar. Today you will be taking to Thekkady. Reach in Thekkady, check into the hotel and have some rest. Later in the day, the tour itinerary takes you out for a jungle safari in the famous Periyar Tiger Reserve which is also known as Periyar National Park. This wildlife sanctuary is the perfect place where you stand a chance to spot exotic flora and fauna in their natural habitat. As the sun sets, then go check out the bustling local market of a nearby town Kumily where you can shop for various variety of spices and make the most of your brief Kerala family Thekkady.', 'highlight of tour', 'After a healthy breakfast check out form the hotel of Thekkady. Today you will be taking to Kochi. Another scenic road journey and another chance for you and your family to fully enjoy road travel in picturesque landscape of Kerala. Known majorly for its vitality and vibrancy, Kochi is one of the most sought after tourist destinations in Kerala. Post your arrival in Kochi, you will check-in to your houseboat. This tour itinerary lets you enjoy exploring famous tourist places of Kochi including Fort Kochi, Mattancherry Palace, St. Francis Church, Kerala Kathakali Centre, Santa Cruz Cathedral Basilica and more with your family. Walk at the Marine Drive in Kochi during evening offers a perfect experience of sunset views. Later by evening you will be escort back to hotel and stay overnight at the hotel in Kochi.', 'departure', 'After a healthy breakfast check out from the houseboat of Kochi. Today you will be taking to back for dropping to Kochi Railway station/Airport for onward journey with a great memory.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 1, 0),
(7, 'adventure', 'A boisterous Bali vacation', '2023-06-13', 'indian', 'bali', 'package_imgs/960x0.jpg', 'It isn’t every day that you get to spend quality time with the whole family. As everyone gets older, their lives get busier and it becomes difficult to simply sit down, catch up and really get to know how they’re doing. One of the things you could do to fix that is a classic family vacation.\r\n\r\nWith our Bali packages deals for family, the important details of what to do and where to go will be sorted out quite smoothly. Here’s a glimpse of what’s to come on this journey. The minor details of how you will travel from place to place won’t be your headache on this tour, so feel comfortable to let your guard down and enjoy each others’ company with our family deal packages to Bali.', 29999, 6, 7, 'arrival', 'As you land in Bali, the tour starts in earnest as you are moved from the airport to the hotel. Once you are checked-in, spend the day how you’d like until the day draws to a close with an overnight stay.', 'Sightseeing: Adventure Sports and Temples', 'On the second day of the tour, we really pick up the pace. First, we take to the seas for some exciting adventure sports. Enjoy a brisk ride along the sea in a speedboat, or a deep dive into the sea to witness the gorgeous marine life. Take a tour around some of Bali’s most iconic cultural monuments, the temples of Uluwatu and Tanah Lot.', 'spa day', 'After the previous day’s sense of adventure, enjoy a soothing day today. Get a massage and come back to your hotel refreshed and ready for the following day’s events.', 'kintamani', 'A wonderful little village on the northern section of the island, Kintamani is another example of the natural beauty on the island of Bali. Also visit Mount Batur.', 'leisure', 'The fifth day of this tour slows things down. You are free to do as you please throughout the entirety of the day. If you need to get some shopping done, this would be the day to do it.', 'departure', 'Finally, the tour draws to a close. Check-out from the hotel and head to the airport.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, 1),
(8, 'honeymoon', 'Romantic Bali', '2023-04-29', 'ahmedabad', 'bali', 'package_imgs/baali.jpg', 'Book an exotic 5 nights 6 days Bali honeymoon package for an indelible holiday experience in the Indonesian island. Saunter amidst forested volcanic mountains, beaches, rice paddies, and coral reefs with your loved one beside you. Enjoy a tropical getaway with your partner-for-life and indulge in a slew of activities such temple visits or beach walks with our Bali romantic tour package for 6 days.', 32999, 6, 5, 'Kuta: Arrival and leisure day', 'Your day is at leisure and you can spend it as per your desires. Wash off your weariness or explore the local markets in the evening. Enjoy a romantic dinner and come back to the hotel for a good night’s rest.', 'Kuta: Scintillating Tanah Lot temple tour', 'Savor a hearty breakfast and proceed for local sightseeing in Bali. Visit Tanah Lot Temple - the most famous landmark on the island - and begin your honeymoon on a happy high. You will also be taken to the Bedugul village where you can relax beside the Bratan Lake.', 'Kuta: Thrilling watersports with the loved one', 'Gorge upon a hearty breakfast and prepare for your transfer to Tanjung Benoa beach for a day full of merriment. Enjoy a thrilling day with your better half and choose from a range of watersports such as parasailing, banana boat ride, jet ski, and snorkeling. Also, visit the Turtle Island by glass bottom boat. If you are lucky, you will also get to spot a green turtle in its natural habitat and revel in the quaint surroundings.', 'Kuta: Transfer to villa', 'Enjoy a full day tour of Kintamani Volcano and Ubud Village on your Bali Ubud honeymoon tour\r\n\r\nSavor a delectable breakfast and proceed for a full day tour of Kintamani Volcano and Ubud Village. Revel in the scenic beauty of the Crater Lake & Batur mountain, which is also considered to be a sacred mountain according to Hindu beliefs.', 'Kuta: Enjoy leisure day', 'Enjoy your day at leisure on the penultimate day of your honeymoon in Bali\r\n\r\nGorge upon a delicious breakfast on the penultimate day of your Bali package and plan out your leisure day as per your desires. You can relax with a therapeutic Balinese spa, which will rejuvenate your mind and body. Also shop for souvenirs in Kuta for your loved ones back home.', 'Kuta: Time to bid goodbye', 'Your 6-day Bali honeymoon itinerary comes to an end\r\n\r\nAfter a delectable breakfast, it is time to check-out from the hotel. Get transferred to the airport for your journey back home.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, 1),
(9, 'international', 'dream dubai  trip', '2023-05-24', 'ahmedabad', 'dubai', 'package_imgs/Burj_Khalifa_2021_2PS3SK1.jpg', 'Get a chance to explore the awe-inspiring sights and sounds of Dubai with our 4 nights and 5 days Budget trip to Dubai. Dubai is a rich amalgam of culture, tradition and cosmopolitan infused with modernity. Renowned as the shopping capital of the world, Dubai offers an eclectic mix of shopping experiences, entertainment, adventure in Arabian desert and cruises in the ocean. With our Budget Trip to Dubai, experience the best of this desert kingdom as you cruise on Dhow Marina, visit the Burj Al Arab and the man Made palm island Jumeirah along with witnessing the Arabic Tanoura Dance show and more.', 85000, 5, 6, 'Arrive Dubai- Dhow Marina Cruise', 'Upon your arrival at the Dubai Airport, our tour representative will escort you to one of our listed hotels. Check-in at the hotel where you can relax in the comfort room. The rest of the afternoon is at your leisure you can spend the whole day relaxing and napping. Later in the evening you will enjoy your time in the Marina Dhow Cruise. A \'Dhow\' is a traditional wooden vessel that has been renovated into a floating restaurant that\'s why it is one of the most popular dinner cruises in Dubai.', 'Dubai – Dubai City tour + Desert Safari', 'On the 2nd Day of the Dubai trip you will head for the Dubai City tour and later in the afternoon, you will enjoy your time in the Desert Safari. Dubai is simply one of the best places to visit in the world.', 'Dubai – Global Village Tour', 'After having breakfast in the hotel, you will be taken to Global Village. Located Sheikh in Mohammed Bin Zayed Road Exit 37, Global Village is renowned for its cultural vibes and amazing shopping experiences. The village also offers a range of dining experiences to delight the connoisseurs of food along with adrenaline-pumping entertainment, adventure, and roller coaster rides. Global Village offers a fulsome entertainment experience to families, youths, and kids alike.', 'Dubai – Day is free', 'After breakfast in the Hotel The day is at your leisure. You can spend the whole day relaxing and napping. In the evening you can move out of the hotel for shopping. The world\'s first rotating skyscrapers and the most amazing man-made archipelagos along with palm-shaped islands. You can enjoy shopping here with your loved ones. Overnight stay at the hotel in Dubai.', 'Depart Dubai', 'The delightful Dubai tour ends today. Enjoy a leisurely breakfast. Later in the afternoon check out of the day and opt for some last-minute shopping. In the evening, get assisted transfer to the airport to board your flight for home.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, 1),
(10, 'international', 'thailand trip', '2023-05-18', 'ahmedabad', 'thailand', 'package_imgs/thailand-tour-package-4-days-1595.jpeg', 'If you are looking for a Pattaya Bangkok tour, we offer tastefully crafted packages for you. Visit the beautiful destinations in Thailand and enjoy a fun-filled vacation. Enjoy the Coral Island tour by speedboat and the famous Alcazar Cabaret Show in Pattaya. Explore the beautiful city of Bangkok, its bustling streets, food, and more. Witness the breathtaking landscapes of palm trees, crystal clear waters, and sun-soaked beaches.', 49999, 4, 5, 'Arrival in Pattaya', 'Welcome Travelers! As soon as you arrive at the Pattaya airport, our representative will pick you up and transfer you to your pre-booked hotel. Upon reaching, check-in and relax for some time. Get ready in the evening for an exotic performance at the Alcazar Cabaret show. Afterward, get back to the hotel for a comfortable overnight sleep.', 'Coral Island Tour', 'post a scrumptious breakfast, get ready for the Coral Island tour via speedboat. Treat your eyes to the crystal clear cyan-colored waters and click pictures for memories. Witness the gardens of coral reefs and vibrant fishes in the lagoon. Savor a delectable lunch at the beach under the golden sun and then, spend time chilling at the beach. After such an amazing experience, return to the hotel and retire for the day. Hop onto the bed, get comfy, and sleep the night away.', 'Pattaya - Bangkok', 'On day 3 of your Bangkok Pattaya tour, after a delicious breakfast, check out from the hotel. You will be transferred to Bangkok. As you reach, get checked in at the hotel and enjoy the remaining day as per your interests. You can go out and explore the local area, markets, and nearby attractions. You can also enjoy the Alcazar Show in Bangkok. Overnight stay at the hotel.', 'Departure from Bangkok', 'Your Pattaya Bangkok tour of 4 days and 3 nights comes to an end today. Have a leisurely breakfast and get transferred to the airport. Catch a flight back home with unforgettable memories of the Thailand tour.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, 1),
(11, 'inter', 'Magnificent Singapore', '2023-06-23', 'banglore', 'singapore', 'package_imgs/singapore-9.jpeg', 'he charm of Singapore reflects through its unique culture, lush greenery, and architectural wonders. You can plan your International tour at this dreamy destination to get the best holiday experience. We have a well-designed 5 days Singapore tour package that will give you a new adventure every day. With this tour package, you can explore various attractions throughout your journey.\r\n\r\nThis tour package will take you on a ride to cover the prime attractions of Singapore, such as Sentosa Island, Singapore Zoo, Universal Studio, and many more. There is so much to do and see when you are in Singapore, so peruse this itinerary for more details. Book this 4 nights 5 days Singapore tour package to have a luxurious and comfortable experience that leaves indelible marks on your heart.', 109000, 5, 4, 'Arriving in Singapore', 'This Singapore tour commences as you arrive at Singapore airport. After arriving, you will clear your immigration and get a transfer to your pre-booked hotel. Once you reach the hotel, you will complete the check-in process and move towards your room. Later, you will rest for a while before moving out for the Singapore Zoo.', 'Sightseeing Tour of Sentosa Island', 'Start the day with a healthy breakfast in your hotel and enjoy the leisure activity. Then, you will take a Sentosa Twilight Tour that covers a one-way cable car ride, admission ticket, Madame Tussauds 5 in 1, Lunge, and Skyride in the afternoon. Moreover, you will have the opportunity to explore many attractions like the SEA Aquarium, Sentosa Beaches, Adventure Cove Waterpark, etc.', 'Visit Universal Studio', 'Rise and shine in the morning and welcome the day with a refreshing breakfast in the hotel. After finishing your breakfast, you will be taken to Universal Studios. It is one of the most popular attractions in Singapore. You will explore various theme zones in this universal studio on the third day of your Singapore tour. This studio features Hollywood, New York, Sci-Fi City, Ancient Egypt, The Lost World, Far Far Away, and Madagascar zones.', 'Garden by The Bay with Marina Bay Sand Sky Park', 'Wake up early in the morning with a healthy breakfast and be ready to fill your heart with double fun. Today, you will take a fascinating Garden By The Bay tour with Marina Bay Sands Sky Park. Firstly, you will explore Garden by the Bay; a nature park spread to 101 hectares. Next, you will admire the supertrees-like structure that dominates the garden\'s landscape.', 'Departure from Singapore', 'You will welcome the morning vibes with a healthy breakfast on this day. After finishing your breakfast, you will have free time until the tour representative reaches the hotel to give you a transfer to the airport. Our representative will make all arrangements in advance to provide you with ease and a comfortable journey.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 1, 0, 1),
(12, 'inter', 'Budget Trip to Maldives', '2023-08-10', 'ahmedabad', 'maldives', 'package_imgs/budget-trip-to-maldives-1360.png', 'This Maldives tour package from India is crafted in a way so that you will have ample time to adhere to each holiday element in the Maldives, including cultural sightseeing, heritage sightseeing, local experience, watersports fun. This trip\'s starting and ending point will be Malé, and once you arrive at the resort, all the days will be at your leisure. \r\n\r\nWe have included 3-star accommodation in this package with speedboat pickup/drop meals. The accommodation will be in 3 variants -  sea view room, beachfront, standard, superior. Feel free to customize your trip if you want. Meanwhile, take a look at this suggested budget Maldives trip itinerary!', 50000, 5, 4, 'Maldives: Arrival at Malé International Airport', 'fter landing at Velana International Airport in Malé, our representative would welcome you with warm greetings. After giving your luggage, followed by loading in the speedboat, enjoy the speedboat ride for a few minutes to get transferred to your accommodation.', 'Malé: Day Reserved For Watersports', 'Treat your tastebuds to the flavorsome breakfast, and then head out to spend the full day at the beaches. Whether you are with your soulmate or family or friends, or even solo, fun frolic moments are guaranteed because the sand is pristine at the beaches of Malé.', 'Malé: Enjoy the Day At Your Convenience', 'Marvel the elegance of dozens of the Mosques in the Malé. Learn about the historical treasures of Maldives at the Museums. Inhale fresh air amidst the lush greenery at the Sultan Park (Rasrani Bageecha), and end your evening with a shopping excursion to the local markets to buy Maldivan handicrafts and stuff.', 'Malé: Another Day to Get Pampered With Relaxation', 'Start your morning with an appetizing breakfast and pick the opportunity to enjoy day 4 at your own preferences. This will be the second last day of a 4 nights and 5 days budget trip to the Maldives so explore the island on foot because the whole of Malé city could be easily covered within the 45 minutes (approx.) of foot expedition.', 'depart from maldives', 'Bow down your head at the sapphire blue waters of the last time all around you because, after a lip-smacking breakfast and check-out procedure, you will be escorted to the Velana International Airport to fly back to your home with a bag full of Maldives holiday memories.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, 1),
(13, 'international', 'Paris With Disneyland Tour', '2023-06-22', 'india', 'paris', 'package_imgs/paris-with-disneyland-685.jpeg', 'Paris With Disneyland tour package is a well planned 4 nights and 5 days itinerary that lets you explore Paris to the fullest. The tour will take you to iconic buildings like Eiffel Tower, a prominent attraction to be watched while in Paris. Also, enjoy a visit to the various structures built during the Napoleonic era to understand the city\'s rich culture and history.', 90000, 5, 4, 'Paris', 'Upon arriving at the Paris airport, meet our representative, who\'ll escort you to one of our listed hotels. Check-in at the hotel. Spend the day relaxing in the comfortable surroundings of the hotel room. In the evening you may take a leisurely walk to explore Paris, the romantic capital of the world. Then, experience an unforgettable evening by attending the Lido Show, the famous French lounge in the Champs Elysee. A major attraction of the show is witnessing an impressive performance of the Bluebell Girls and the Lido Boy Dancers. Later return to the hotel for dinner and an overnight stay.', 'Paris: Panoramic City Tour', 'The following day, after breakfast, embark on a sightseeing tour of Paris. Today, you will visit some beautiful Napoleonic-era structures, including Champs Elysees. Next, visit the iconic Eiffel Tower, one of the most famous attractions of Paris. It is famed for being the tallest building present in Paris. Later in the day, you may pay a visit to the Musee du Louvre, originally a royal fortress converted into a museum that houses more than 35,000 works of art. Drive past the Louvre Museum. Also, pay a visit to Place Vendôme, Cathedral of Notre Dame, and Comédie Française. In the evening, return to the hotel to enjoy a lavish dinner and a comfortable overnight stay.', 'Paris: Disneyland', 'The 3rd day of the tour is reserved for a full-day excursion to Disneyland. The day will surely be full of fun, entertainment, and adventure. There are numerous rides in Disney Park to make you feel the adrenaline rush under your skin. Also, enjoy visiting the beautiful Walt Disney Studio Park, where you can see various stunt shows and watch a film being shot. Watching real-life sets where famous movies were created will surely delight you. Finally, enjoy dinner and an overnight stay at the hotel.', 'Paris', 'Post breakfast today, and the day is free for leisure activities. So you may move out to explore Paris on your own. You will find ornate and elegant architecture at every turn during the tour. Seeing how these striking landmarks are connected and aligned through wide boulevards and open spaces offering magnificent views is impressive. After exploring Paris, the \"City of Lights\" return to the hotel to enjoy a sumptuous lip-smacking dinner and an overnight stay at the hotel.', 'Depart Paris', 'In the morning, after breakfast, get transferred to Paris CDG airport on a SIC (Seat- In-Coach) basis to board a flight for your onward destination.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, 1),
(14, 'spiritual', 'Chardham Yatra', '2023-07-27', 'ahmedabad', 'chardham', 'package_imgs/images.jpg', 'Chardham Yatra is the staircase that leads pilgrims step by step closer to salvation. Beginning from Yamunotri, the sojourn leads to Gangotri, Kedarnath, and concludes on Badrinath. These four holy sites are part of the Chota Char Dham of Uttarakhand and are highly revered by Hindus.\r\n\r\nBegin the spiritual journey of Chardham Yatra by helicopter in 2023, and get a memorable experience in Uttarakhand. For the total cost of the Chardham Yatra package, you can contact us.', 39000, 6, 5, 'Arrival and Briefing', 'your holy tour begins in Dehradun. On arrival at Dehradun airport or railway station, meet and greet our representative and get an assisted transfer to the hotel. Once reached, complete the check-in formalities, and relax. Later in the evening, our representative will be briefing about the tour and will hand over Duffel Bags for carrying the necessary luggage for the journey ahead. After the briefing, surrender yourself to the world of dreams.', 'Dehradun - Kharsali (Yamunotri Temple)', 'The next morning checkout from the hotel at Dehradun around 6:00 am. Today, you will be transferred to Sahastradhara Helipad, from where you will officially begin your holy yatra. After reaching Sahastradhara Helipad enjoy your chopper ride to Kharsali. On arrival, you will be welcomed and transferred to your respective hotel by our ground crew. After reaching the hotel complete your check-in formalities and enjoy your delicious breakfast. Later you will be taken for the darshan by Palki/Pony. Enjoy a hot spring bath at Yamunotri Temple. Post Darshan, pay a visit to Shani Temple and seek blessings. After an amazing day, get over the journey fatigue with a sound sleep.', 'Kharsali - Harsil (Gangotri Temple)', 'Greet the early morning sun, check out from the hotel around 6:30 am, and get ready to catch your next destination, which is Gangotri Dham/Temple. Today you will be transferred to the Kharsali helipad, on arrival get ready to enjoy a 30 minutes chopper ride to reach Harsil. On arrival, you will get an assisted transfer to your hotel. After reaching, complete your check-in formalities, relax and enjoy the delicious breakfast. Later get ready to pay a visit to the Gangotri Temple.', 'Harsil - Sersi (Kedarnath Temple)', 'On day 4 of your Chardham Yatra by Helicopter tour, wake up early in the morning, enjoy your delicious breakfast, and complete the checkout formalities. Leave the hotel around 7 am. Today you will be transferred to the Harsil helipad, on arrival get ready to enjoy a 30 minutes chopper ride to reach Sersi.', 'ersi (Kedarnath Temple) - Badrinath (Badrinath Tem', 'The next morning savor some toothsome breakfast and checkout from the hotel around 8 am. Today, you will be transferred to Badrinath via helicopter from Sersi. After reaching Badrinath you will be assisted to your hotel. On reaching the hotel, complete your check-in formalities and relax. Badrinath is one of the pre-eminent pilgrimage places among Hindus, the temple is dedicated to Lord Vishnu.', 'Badrinath - Dehradun', 'Wake up to an appetizing breakfast and complete your checkout formalities. As your Char Dham Yatra 2022 by helicopter concludes here, you will be transferred to Sahastradhara. After reaching Sahastradhara, you will have an assisted transfer to the hotel at Dehradun for the collection of your respective luggage from the cloakroom. Later you will be transferred to the airport/railway station for your journey back home.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 1, 0),
(15, 'spiritual', 'kedarnath yatra', '2023-05-24', 'ahmedabad', 'kedarnath', 'package_imgs/download.jpg', 'Kedarnath Temple is among 12 Jyotirlingas in India and is also the holiest Hindu pilgrimage site in India. Located in the state of Uttarakhand, many people of the Hindu religion desire to take its yatra. Tourism of India offers a wide range of Kedarnath Yatra packages from Haridwar for people who seek blessings from Lord Shiva. Not only from India, but pilgrims from outside the country visit Kedarnath to pay their respects to the Supreme Being.', 51000, 4, 3, 'Guptkashi: Arrival', 'After arrival at Haridwar, our representative will welcome you and drive you towards Guptkashi. Upon arrival, check-in to the hotel and enjoy the day at leisure before commencing the Kedarnath Yatra. Have dinner and enjoy a comfortable overnight stay at the hotel.', 'Kedarnath: Darshan of Kedarnath Temple', 'After a wholesome breakfast, check-out from the hotel and proceed towards Sonprayag. Reach Gaurikund, the starting point for the trek to Kedarnath. Once arrived, check-in to the hotel and get ready for the trek. Begin 7 hours (approx.) trek from the base of Gaurikund to Kedarnath Temple. Pay your respect to Lord Shiva and take part in the evening aarti here. After the aarti completes, drive back to the hotel for dinner and overnight stay.', 'Rudraprayag/Srinagar: Shiva Abhishek', 'Arise early morning, take a bath, and get ready for the 4.45 am ‘Abhishek’ to Lord Shiva. After the puja, enter Garbha Griha, where the idol of the Lord resides, and seek His blessings. Have breakfast and check-out from the hotel. Start the return trek from Kedarnath to Sonprayag and drive towards Rudraprayag. After reaching, check-in to the hotel and rest. Have dinner and enjoy an overnight stay at the hotel.', 'Haridwar: Departure', 'After a delicious breakfast, check-out from the hotel, and drive towards the ‘Yoga Capital’, Rishikesh. En route witness Devprayag Sangam, the confluences where the Alaknanda and Bhagirathi rivers converge. Upon reaching Rishikesh, visit Lakshman Jhula or stroll through the markets of Rishikesh for souvenirs. Later, drive towards Haridwar for your onward destination with delightful memories.', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 1, 0, 1, 0);

